        <Parent_String>conveyors [300024559], moving and transporting machinery [300162805], moving and transporting equipment [300024783], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
